局部坐标法:
summon armor_stand (x) (y) (z) {tag:1}
//此处的x,y,z为起始坐标
execute as @a[tag=1] run execute at @a[tag=1] run tp @s ~ ~ ~ (a) (b)
//此处的a,b为垂直、水平旋转角度

执行n次(n为粒子数量):
execute at @a[tag=1] run summon armor_stand ^ ^ ^1 {tag:2}
execute at @a[tag=1] run particle ...
kill @e[tag=1]
tag @a[tag=2] add 1
tag @a[tag=2] remove 2

最后kill @e[tag=1]即可

